column1: # Main Bill of Materials (BOM) for Node.js Quantum Hardware KiCAD Project
This file contains the main Bill of Materials (BOM) for the Node.js Quantum Hardware project.
The BOM provides a detailed list of all the components used in the project
column4: and supplier information. It is crucial for procurement and manufacturing processes.

column1: To view or edit this BOM
column2: open it in any spreadsheet software like Microsoft Excel or Google Sheets.

column1: We use Git for version control. Please make sure to update tests as appropriate.
Regular backups of the BOM files are stored in the Backups directory.
